  "texts": [
    "First, we empirically evaluate the classification accuracy of GPT-3.5, GPT-4, and Llama 2 using an alternative prompting method, i.e., contextual prompting (vs. instructive prompts which are used in Experiment 1), on eight datasets.",
    "We ensure a balance between Twitter and non-Twitter datasets and choose datasets that have demonstrated high, medium, and low accuracy levels in the binary and three-class experiment.",
    "This selection allows us to examine the impact of prompting methods across varying levels of performance.",
    "In sum, we evaluate 1,592 text documents.",
    "Second, we repeat the process on the same textual documents using a few-shot prompting method."
  ],
